				<wikidot:authorName>Uncle Nicolini</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3487700</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The idea of Trump as a literal and metaphorical void is an interesting one. There's a lot of talk about the man but what <em>is</em> the man? It feels like he's more defined by the people around him and public perception than himself, or has he become what the public perception thinks of him?</p> <p>Interesting article.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
